---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout lang="en" title="Home" description="First Up Weddings. Cinematic wedding films that preserve real emotions. Your day, told like a film.">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[90vh] flex items-center justify-center bg-brand-warm overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-warm/30 via-brand-warm/50 to-brand-cream z-10"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <!-- Hero background. To replace with a video later, swap this gradient div for:
           <video src="/hero-wedding.mp4" poster="/hero-wedding-poster.jpg" autoplay muted loop playsinline preload="metadata" class="w-full h-full object-cover"></video> -->
      <div class="w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-warm via-brand-cream to-brand-warm opacity-60"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-20 text-center px-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-heading font-normal leading-tight mb-6 text-brand-dark">
        Your day. Your film.<br /><span class="text-brand-accent">Your story.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-brand-text max-w-xl mx-auto mb-10 font-light leading-relaxed">
        Cinematic wedding films that preserve real emotions.
      </p>
      <a href="/en/contact" class="btn-primary">Get in touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- EMOTIONALER INTROTEXT -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-brand-cream">
    <div class="container-narrow text-center">
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-heading font-normal text-brand-dark leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        A wedding film by First Up Weddings captures exactly the feeling YOU want to remember.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-6 text-brand-accent font-heading text-lg italic">Cinematic. Honest. Yours forever.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WAS EINEN GUTEN HOCHZEITSFILM AUSMACHT -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-brand-warm">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading text-center text-brand-dark mb-16">What makes a great wedding film</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-heading text-brand-accent mb-3">Real moments, never staged</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-text leading-relaxed">The most beautiful scenes happen when no one is thinking about the camera. A great wedding film captures exactly that — unfiltered, honest, cinematic.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-heading text-brand-accent mb-3">Emotion, not documentation</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-text leading-relaxed">A wedding film is not a recording. It is a film that lets you feel how the day felt: the heartbeat, the anticipation, the relief, the joy.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-heading text-brand-accent mb-3">Cinematic visual language</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-text leading-relaxed">Your film looks and feels like a proper film — with deliberate camera work, natural light, and a visual language that carries your story.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-heading text-brand-accent mb-3">Always with you</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-text leading-relaxed">Photos preserve moments. Only a film preserves the voices, the laughter, the music, the atmosphere — everything that made this day your day.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WIE ICH ARBEITE -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-brand-warm">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading text-center text-brand-dark mb-16">From first meeting to finished film.</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 text-center">
        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl font-heading text-brand-accent mb-4">01</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-heading text-brand-dark mb-3">We get to know each other</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-text leading-relaxed">A relaxed conversation, by video or in person. We learn who you are and what matters most to you.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl font-heading text-brand-accent mb-4">02</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-heading text-brand-dark mb-3">Your wedding day</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-text leading-relaxed">On the day itself, we are quietly there. No posed direction — only real moments, captured cinematically.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl font-heading text-brand-accent mb-4">03</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-heading text-brand-dark mb-3">Your film</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-text leading-relaxed">After the wedding, your film takes shape in careful post-production — with everything that made the day yours.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center mt-12">
        <a href="/en/your-day" class="text-sm text-brand-accent hover:text-brand-accent-hover transition-colors font-heading tracking-wide">Discover the full journey →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- NICHT NUR HOCHZEITEN -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-brand-warm">
    <div class="container-narrow text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading text-brand-dark mb-6">More than just the wedding day.</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-text max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Weddings are at the heart of our work. But your story doesn't begin at the altar. Engagement films, proposal coverage, engagement shoots as motion pieces, save-the-date videos: whenever it's about you and your story, we'll find a way to capture it. Just reach out.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MEIN VERSPRECHEN -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-brand-cream">
    <div class="container-narrow text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading text-brand-dark mb-12">What you can expect from us</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-left">
        <div class="bg-brand-warm p-8">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-heading text-brand-dark mb-3">Discreet presence</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-text leading-relaxed">We are there without being in the way. Your guests should enjoy your day, not navigate around a camera.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-warm p-8">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-heading text-brand-dark mb-3">Personal contact</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-text leading-relaxed">From the first conversation to the finished film, you speak directly with us. No hand-offs, no detours — only filmmakers who know your story.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-warm p-8">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-heading text-brand-dark mb-3">Cinematic standard</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-text leading-relaxed">Our background is in film, not in event documentation. You feel it in the visual language, the editing, the atmosphere.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-warm p-8">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-heading text-brand-dark mb-3">Reliability</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-text leading-relaxed">Clear agreements, firm dates, transparent communication. On your day, the only thing you need to focus on is each other.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABSCHLUSS CTA -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-brand-cream">
    <div class="container-narrow text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading text-brand-dark mb-6">Your day deserves to be remembered.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-text max-w-xl mx-auto mb-10">
        Tell us about your wedding, and we'll show you how your film could look.
      </p>
      <a href="/en/contact" class="btn-primary">Request a quote</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
